The President of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee: Firmly Believes that China has the Ability to Host the Winter Olympics in a Special Period - Xinhua News Agency, Sarajevo, December 11th. The President of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee, Kveticić, recently stated that Bosnia is very much looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and firmly believes that China has the ability to host the Winter Olympics in a special period. Recently, China's Ambassador to Bosnia and Herzegovina, Ji Ping, met with the President of the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee, Kveticić, at the Sarajevo Olympic Center. During the meeting, Kveticić positively evaluated the relationship between Bosnia and China and stated that he visited China during the 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics and was deeply impressed by China's excellent organizational work. He firmly believes that China has the ability to host the Winter Olympics in a special period; Bosnia is very much looking forward to the Beijing Winter Olympics and the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee is actively organizing participation; Bosnia hopes to use this as an opportunity to carry out more extensive exchanges and cooperation with China in the field of sports. Ji Ping stated that Bosnia and China have a special "Olympic link". The 1984 Winter Olympics were successfully held in Sarajevo, and in two months, the 2022 Beijing Winter Olympics will also be held, presenting a simple, safe, and exciting event to the world. It is hoped that the two countries will deepen their exchanges and cooperation in winter sports events, athlete training, and other aspects, and the Chinese Embassy in Bosnia and Herzegovina is willing to continue to play a bridge role, using the Beijing Winter Olympics as an opportunity to deepen the cultural exchange between the two countries, so that the people of the two countries "look forward together", and wish the athletes of Bosnia and Herzegovina good performance in Beijing. Before the meeting, the Bosnia and Herzegovina Olympic Committee held the "10th Annual Best Athlete" award ceremony, and Chi Ping was invited as a guest to award the best young athlete in Bosnia and Herzegovina. The Beijing Winter Olympics promotional video was played repeatedly on the scene.
